'''Gha-Mu''' (''Small Flowery Miao'', ''Blue Hmong'') are an ethnic group in [[China]]. They are from [[Guizhou]] and belong to the [[Hmong people]]. Many of them are Christians. The number of persons within this group likely exceeds 100,000. Their language is the [[Hmong language]] [[Small Flowery Miao]]; [[Large Flowery Miao]] is another, of the [[A-Hmao]]. 

