The '''Zakar Zai''' is a branch of the [[Mengal]] tribe of [[Pakistan]]. They live in various areas of [[Balochistan (Pakistan)|Balochistan]] and [[Sindh Province|Sindh]], but the majority are in the districts of Nushki, [[Kalat District|Kalat]] and [[Quetta District|Quetta]], as well as in [[Khuzdar]] and [[Surab, Pakistan|Surab]].

